which method type..
			--- controller method..
			


Handermapping table -- spring -- at the time spring app instantation

requestmapping - method type -- fullyqualified controllernames --- methodname

"{[/list],methods=[GET]}" "ProductController.fetchAllProducts()

"{[/delete],methods=[POST]}" "ProductController.deleteProduct()

"{[/save],methods=[GET]}" "ProductController.persisteProduct()

"{[/update],methods=[GET]}" "ProductController.updateProduct()
